The Expiration Monitor for Azure Secrets (AZE) app allows you to monitor the expiration of Azure secrets within a specific tenant, as well as the expiration of additional manually entered tokens or certificates. If it expires soon, the app will send a notification via email.

Press ALT + Q and type "AZE" to see a list of the involved features: 
